[F]We kick and cuss and scream and shout
[C]Until we forget what we're fighting about
[G7]Kiss make up and make love some more
[C]Cause all is fair in love and war
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_verse: Verse 3}
Well [F]anything goes when it comes to love  
Someone's going down when push comes to [C]shove
It's a [F]fight to the finish with no holds barred
If someone winds up with a broken heart
That's [G7]tough that's real tough
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_verse: Verse 4}
